<title>Previo a la unidad</title>
<!-- <title>Exploración</title> -->
<title component="metadata">Alineado con <xref ref="gra3-uni2-secA" text="title"/></title>
<!-- <title component="metadata">Alineado con <xref ref="lec-VVVVVV" text="title"/></title> -->

<statement>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-151452.svg">
    <shortdescription>A centimeter ruler with 2 line segments labeled A and B.</shortdescription>
  </image>
  <p>Usa la regla de centímetros para encontrar las longitudes de los dos segmentos de recta A y B. Explica tu razonamiento.</p>
</statement>

<solution>
  <p>[++++++++++++++++++++]</p>
  <p><m>9 - 3 = 6</m></p>
  <p>Segment A is 7 centimeters long since it starts at 0 and goes to 7. Segment B is 6 centimeters long since it starts at 3 and goes to 9 and .</p>
</solution>

</exercise>
